Package ch.aaap.harvestclient.domain.pagination

Interface PaginatedList

@TypeAdapters(fieldNamingStrategy=true) @Immutable public interface PaginatedList
Holds any type of list from Harvest. We use the fact that missing JSON fields will be set to null
